{"tid":1791630,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"希望大家醒一醒 家陣係文革2.0","createTime":"2019-12-21T04:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T03:07:45.000Z","uid":17554,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"267b9cd5007695e06f136bc4a95b2e1df53b3279","tid":1791630,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:10:42.000Z","msg":"搞星火-&gt; 秋後算賬 想拎捐款名單 順便借機干預金融自由<br />\n<br />\n搞老師-&gt; 思想控制 要批鬥民主反共勢力 順便植入愛國老師勢力<br />\n<br />\n搞企業-&gt; 經濟控制 要排擠曬反對奶共既企業 同當年打倒私人企業一樣<br />\n<br />\n搞手足 -&gt; 意識形態控制 瘋狂打壓反對聲音<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 家陣已經係文革2.0 又想批鬥知識份子 批鬥民主自由 批鬥市場自由<br />\n<br />\n香港人 醒啦！自古行極權主義既國家都係失敗告終 哪怕只有一點希望 都要繼續努力 革命尚未成功 同志仍需努力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命！ 今生無悔做香港人！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"ec3db50c5c0400dfae03625957f7462caa83e5a4","tid":1791630,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c3be482c810897a162efe4a8bf09cac2dfdf71","tid":1791630,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4b3c6567862626975a9154ae7ba5e7c7df1659","tid":1791630,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\"